Di y l gii thch chi tit v cc li trong log ca ng dng v hng dn cch khc phc:

## 1. Li "BulkCursor - Unable to get window because the remote process is dead"

**Gii thch:**
- Li ny xy ra khi ng dng c gng truy cp mt cursor nhng qu trnh cung cp cursor b kt thc
- Thng xy ra khi c vn v qun l b nh hoc khi ContentProvider b crash

**Cch khc phc:**
- Kim tra vic ng cursor ng cch trong code
- m bo rng vic truy vn ContentProvider c thc hin trong thread ring
- Thm x l ngoi l khi truy vn database

```kotlin
// Thm try-catch khi lm vic vi cursor
try {
 cursor = contentResolver.query(uri, projection, selection, selectionArgs, sortOrder)
 // X l cursor
} catch (e: Exception) {
 Log.e("Database", "Error querying content provider", e)
} finally {
 cursor?.close()
}
```

## 2. Li "No package ID 76 found for resource ID 0x760b000f"

**Gii thch:**
- ng dng ang c gng truy cp mt resource vi ID 0x760b000f nhng khng tm thy trong package ID 76
- Thng xy ra khi s dng th vin hoc ti nguyn khng tn ti

**Cch khc phc:**
- Kim tra cc dependency trong file build.gradle
- Cp nht version ca cc th vin ang s dng
- Xem li m ngun tm tham chiu n resource khng tn ti

```gradle:app/build.gradle
dependencies {
 // m bo cc th vin c cp nht
 implementation 'androidx.core:core-ktx:1.12.0'
 implementation 'androidx.appcompat:appcompat:1.6.1'
 // Thm cc dependency khc...
}
```

## 3. Li "Failed to bind to measurement service"

**Gii thch:**
- Dch v o lng qung co (adservices) khng kh dng
- Li lin quan n AdServices API ca Android

**Cch khc phc:**
- m bo thit b/my o ang chy c Google Play Services
- Cp nht version Google Play Services trong app
- Thm x l trng hp dch v khng kh dng

```kotlin
try {
 // Code s dng adservices
} catch (e: Exception) {
 Log.e("AdServices", "Service unavailable", e)
 // X l khi khng c dch v
}
```

## 4. Li "Service connection failed: cf{statusCode=UNKNOWN_ERROR_CODE(7777)..."

**Gii thch:**
- Firebase Analytics (FA) khng th kt ni n dch v
- M li 7777 l li khng xc nh

**Cch khc phc:**
- Cp nht Firebase SDK ln phin bn mi nht
- Kim tra li cu hnh Firebase trong d n
- m bo file google-services.json ng v c cp nht

```gradle:app/build.gradle
dependencies {
 // Cp nht Firebase SDK
 implementation platform('com.google.firebase:firebase-bom:32.7.2')
 implementation 'com.google.firebase:firebase-analytics'
}
```

## 5. Li "PersistentConnection - Firebase Database connection was forcefully killed..."

**Gii thch:**
- Kt ni Firebase Realtime Database b ngt bi server
- C th do cu hnh URL khng chnh xc hoc quyn truy cp b t chi

**Cch khc phc:**
- Kim tra URL ca Firebase Realtime Database trong cu hnh
- Kim tra quy tc bo mt ca Firebase Database
- Xc minh rng thit b c kt ni internet n nh

```kotlin
// Kim tra v cu hnh Firebase Database URL
val database = FirebaseDatabase.getInstance()
try {
 // Xc minh kt ni
 database.setPersistenceEnabled(true)
 // t timeout di hn
 database.getReference(".info/connected").addValueEventListener(object : ValueEventListener {
 override fun onDataChange(snapshot: DataSnapshot) {
 val connected = snapshot.getValue(Boolean::class.java) ?: false
 Log.d("Firebase", "Connected: $connected")
 }

 override fun onCancelled(error: DatabaseError) {
 Log.e("Firebase", "Database error: ${error.message}")
 }
 })
} catch (e: Exception) {
 Log.e("Firebase", "Configuration error", e)
}
```

## Tng quan gii php

1. **Cp nht tt c cc dependency** ln phin bn mi nht
2. **Kim tra cu hnh Firebase** v m bo file google-services.json ng
3. **X l ngoi l** cho vic truy cp database v service
4. **Kim tra quyn Internet** trong AndroidManifest.xml
5. **m bo device c Google Play Services** cc dch v Firebase hot ng
6. **Kim tra URL Firebase Realtime Database** trong console Firebase

