### Bc 2: Ti v hin th nh t Firebase Storage

```kotlin
import com.bumptech.glide.Glide
import com.google.firebase.storage.FirebaseStorage

// Trong Activity hoc Fragment
fun loadImageFromFirebase() {
 val storage = FirebaseStorage.getInstance()
 val storageRef = storage.reference
 val imageRef = storageRef.child("duong_dan_den_anh/ten_anh.jpg")

 val imageView = findViewById<ImageView>(R.id.imageView)

 // Ti nh bng Glide
 imageRef.downloadUrl.addOnSuccessListener { uri ->
 Glide.with(this)
 .load(uri)
 .placeholder(R.drawable.placeholder_image) // nh hin th trong khi ang ti
 .error(R.drawable.error_image) // nh hin th khi li
 .into(imageView)
 }.addOnFailureListener { exception ->
 // X l khi ti nh tht bi
 Log.e("Firebase", "Li ti nh: ${exception.message}")
 }
}
```

### Bc 3: m bo cu hnh Firebase ng cch

Hy chc chn rng bn cu hnh Firebase cho ng dng ca mnh:
1. Thm file `google-services.json` vo th mc app
2. Cu hnh plugin Firebase trong build.gradle cp project v module

