</user_query>"},{"role":"assistant","content":"# S dng nh t drawable trong Firebase Realtime Database

Khi bn lu tr thng tin v nh trong Firebase Realtime Database, c hai cch tip cn chnh:

## 1. Cch bn ang s dng hin ti

Trong v d hin ti ca bn, bn ang lu tr tn file trong Firebase:

```json
"Data": {
 "Categories": {
 "beverages": {
 "Image": "beverages.png",
 "Name": "Beverages"
 },
```

Vi cch ny, bn cn x l trong code bit liu "beverages.png" ny l:
- nh trong drawable
- Hay nh t Firebase Storage

## 2. Gii php cho nh t drawable

Nu bn mun ch r rng nh l t drawable local, bn c th sa li cu trc d liu Firebase nh sau:

```json
"Data": {
 "Categories": {
 "beverages": {
 "Image": "drawable://beverages",
 "Name": "Beverages"
 },
```

Hoc:

```json
"Data": {
 "Categories": {
 "beverages": {
 "Image": {
 "type": "drawable",
 "name": "beverages"
 },
 "Name": "Beverages"
 },
```

Sau , bn cn sa li code x l ng dn ny:

```kotlin:app/src/main/java/com/example/argapp/Classes/CategoriesList.java
@Override
public void onDataChange(@NonNull DataSnapshot snapshot) {
 for (DataSnapshot itemSnapshot : snapshot.getChildren()) {
 String categoryId = itemSnapshot.child("Id").getValue(String.class);
 String categoryName = itemSnapshot.child("Name").getValue(String.class);
 String categoryImage = itemSnapshot.child("Image").getValue(String.class);

 // Thm x l cho nh drawable
 // Nu nh bt u bng "drawable://" th y l nh local
 if (categoryImage != null && categoryImage.startsWith("drawable://")) {
 // Trch xut tn nh t ng dn (vd: "drawable://beverages" -> "beverages")
 String imageName = categoryImage.substring("drawable://".length());
 // Khng cn thm ".png" v Resource ID khng yu cu phn m rng
 categoryImage = imageName;
 }

 Category category = new Category(categoryId, categoryName, categoryImage);
 m_CategoriesList.add(category);
 }

 callback.onCategoriesFetched(m_CategoriesList);
}
```

## 3. Thay i trong lp Category h tr nh drawable

Bn cn cp nht lp Category chuyn i tn drawable thnh resource ID khi cn hin th nh:

```kotlin
public class Category {
 private String id;
 private String name;
 private String image;

 // Cc hm khi to v getter/setter

 // Phng thc mi ly drawable ID nu nh l drawable
 public int getImageResourceId(Context context) {
 if (image == null) return 0;

 try {
 // Ly resource ID t tn drawable
 return context.getResources().getIdentifier(
 image, "drawable", context.getPackageName());
 } catch (Exception e) {
 return 0; // Tr v 0 nu khng tm thy
 }
 }

 // Phng thc kim tra xem nh c phi l drawable hay khng
 public boolean isDrawable() {
 // Nu khng c "http", "https", hoc "gs://" (Firebase Storage) 
 // th coi nh l drawable
 return image != null && 
 !image.startsWith("http://") && 
 !image.startsWith("https://") && 
 !image.startsWith("gs://");
 }
}
```

## 4. Cch s dng trong Adapter hoc Activity

```kotlin
// Trong adapter hoc activity khi cn hin th nh
ImageView imageView = findViewById(R.id.categoryImage); 
Category category = categories.get(position);

if (category.isDrawable()) {
 // Nu l nh drawable
 int resourceId = category.getImageResourceId(context);
 if (resourceId != 0) {
 imageView.setImageResource(resourceId);
 } else {
 // Fallback khi khng tm thy drawable
 imageView.setImageResource(R.drawable.image_placeholder);
 }
} else {
 // Nu l nh t Firebase Storage hoc URL khc
 Glide.with(context)
 .load(category.getImage())
 .placeholder(R.drawable.image_placeholder)
 .error(R.drawable.error_image)
 .into(imageView);
}
```

Vi cch ny, bn c th lu tr c ng dn n nh drawable v ng dn n nh t Firebase Storage trong cng mt cu trc d liu, v code ca bn s x l vic hin th tng ng."}]}
